text: Sashana Carolyn Campbell (born 2 March 1991) is a Jamaican footballer who plays as a midfielder for Israeli club Maccabi Kishronot Hadera FC and the Jamaica women's national team. ==Career== Campbell attended Darton College and the University of West Florida before embarking on a professional career. https://goargos.com/roster.aspx?rp_id=1883 ==International goals== Scores and results list Jamaica's goal tally first {| class="wikitable" |- !
